  <div class="container-medium">
    <div class="blog-post-body-wrapper">
      <div class="rich-text w-richtext">
        <p>
          Introducing <strong>ESG.Credits</strong>, the cutting-edge API solution that empowers forward-thinking
          institutions to integrate <strong>Environmental</strong>, <strong>Social</strong>, and
          <strong>Governance</strong> (ESG) impact benefits into their digital platforms with ease!
        </p>
        <h2>What is ESG.Credits?</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>ESG.Credits</strong> is a revolutionary API solution by
          <strong>Blockchain Web Services</strong> (BWS) designed to unlock the true potential of sustainable finance. It
          offers unparalleled flexibility in impact reporting, adhering to recognised frameworks such as the International
          Capital Market Association (ICMA) standard or any chosen taxonomy. The API accommodates two tiers of impact categories
          and indicators, supporting any impacted unit and ensuring that your impact reporting can be as granular and specific
          as required.
        </p>
        <h2>How Does It Work?</h2>
        <p>
          With <strong>ESG.Credits</strong>, you can effortlessly calculate impact values on an annual basis or based on
          the term of your financial instruments. The API&#x27;s calculations rely on your green framework or the
          &quot;impact profile&quot; of your green project portfolio, reinforcing the authenticity and transparency of
          your reporting.
        </p>
        <h3>Aligning with Global Sustainability Goals</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>ESG.Credits </strong>allows you to align your initiatives with the United Nations&#x27; Sustainable
          Development Goals (SDGs) classifications, and also the EU Taxonomy Regulation’s Environmental Objectives. By
          associating these goals and objectives with your chosen taxonomy impact categories, you can showcase your
          institution&#x27;s commitment to building a better world.
        </p>
        <h3>Supporting Global Financial Institutions</h3>
        <p>
          The API supports any combination of currencies and languages, catering to the diverse needs of financial
          institutions worldwide. Whether you operate in euros, dollars, English, French or any other currency or
          language, <strong>ESG.Credits has got you covered!</strong>
        </p>
        <h3>Building Trust with Blockchain Technology</h3>
        <p>
          At <strong>BWS</strong>, trust and data integrity are paramount. <strong>ESG.Credits</strong> stores your framework&#x27;s
          <strong>ESG</strong> impact profile on the blockchain, guaranteeing tamper-proof records and helping build trust
          with your stakeholders.
          <a href="http://www.bws.ninja/articles/investment-impact-reporting-unlocking-a-sustainable-future"
            >Learn more.</a
          >
        </p>
        <h3>The Future of Sustainable Finance</h3>
        <p>
          With <strong>ESG.Credits</strong>, your financial institution gains a comprehensive, customisable, and
          efficient way to enhance <strong>ESG</strong> reporting. By embracing this groundbreaking API solution, you position
          yourself ahead in the increasingly important realm of sustainable finance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Join us in the journey towards a greener and more sustainable future. Experience the power of
          <strong>ESG.Credits</strong> API and contribute to a better world for generations to come.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.bws.ninja/marketplace/esg-credits">Learn more</a>, and join the sustainability
          revolution!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
